{"tid":416634,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有無曼谷酒店推薦吓，睇到眼花都唔知邊間好","createTime":"2017-09-28T02:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T16:18:16.000Z","uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5e752f86bd5341a5545c2391dfa9cd8967353285","tid":416634,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:35:21.000Z","msg":"小妹黎緊諗住去曼谷hea 吓，但酒店花多眼亂，睇睇我有d暈。想問吓巴打絲打們有無推薦，我追過post架啦，呢到唔太多人講曼谷酒店，順便當呢個post係酒店些牙post等多d人睇吓都好呀！<br />\n<br />\n小妹揾酒店有幾個條件，希望巴絲有建議吓：<br />\n1. 近BTS <br />\n2. 價錢大概500至700港元<br />\n3.有個靚嘅泳池游吓水 ，可以呃吓like <br />\n4.最好去Big C呀嗰d方便，你知港女要係咁買嘢架啦。"},{"pid":"4db73d4f67f8ae42e3349700dc10f1592d05ed5c","tid":416634,"uid":79953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:46:08.000Z","msg":"去過間叫vic3，唔錯，記得幾平下<br />\n近bts"},{"pid":"1ae5166794161326968cd248877bfda7649ecc11","tid":416634,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:47:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過間叫vic3，唔錯，記得幾平下<br />\n近bts</blockquote><br />\nThank you 巴打！"},{"pid":"c5302f00a3f6de69581361cd6ef7c37da50e926a","tid":416634,"uid":119591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:53:55.000Z","msg":"上次住holiday inn express<br />\n幾好"},{"pid":"69063c11035f6ea5f28acbee4763ec3ef86da82f","tid":416634,"uid":13165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過間叫vic3，唔錯，記得幾平下<br />\n近bts</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係幾方便 新淨 可以一宿"},{"pid":"bf70fa6cddaa95186298ec7efb39a22f9b3dede5","tid":416634,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T11:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次住holiday inn express<br />\n幾好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n泳池掂唔掂架？"},{"pid":"5fdb33e4c2888dfdfbb3715ccb989875f733be97","tid":416634,"uid":28771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:09:50.000Z","msg":"the berkeley hotel pratunam<br />\n係水門市場 5星酒店<br />\n9月頭去做緊promo 500蚊晚<br />\n間房幾大,有泳池,10樓有let's